Package com.sri.ai.grinder.group

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AssociativeCommutativeGroup
    Object representing an associative commutative group.
    AssociativeCommutativeSemiRing
    Object representing an associative commutative semi-ring.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAssociativeCommutativeGroup
    An abstract implementation specifying that toString returns the object's name as extracted from the class name.
    AbstractFunctionBasedGroup
    A group whose related problems are represented as function applications on sets
    (e.g.: sum({{ (on X in Integer) X | X > 0 and X < 5 }})).
    AbstractNumericGroup
    An abstract implementation of groups on numbers, capable of processing symbolic numeric expressions, and leaving the additive operation to be specified by abstract methods.
    AbstractQuantifierBasedGroup
    A group whose related problems are represented by a quantified expression
    (e.g.: for all X in Integer: X > 0 and X < 5).
    Conjunction
    Object representing a group on booleans and conjunction.
    Disjunction
    Object representing a group on booleans and disjunction.
    Max
    Object representing a group on symbolic numbers with the maximum operation.
    Product
    Object representing a group on symbolic numbers with multiplication.
    Sum
    Object representing a group on symbolic numbers with addition.
    SumProduct
    Object representing a group on symbolic numbers with addition.
